<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="23Feb1938"><font color="red">23 February 1938</font> <i>NLCV</i> (from Viscount Carlow to Paul L&eacute;on): Thank you for your letter of 17th February. The binders tell me that we shall have the first consignment of &ldquo;Storiella&rdquo; on Monday the 28th February &hellip; I will at once send two copies to Mr Joyce in Switzerland. </div>
